reviewText: Very hard to follow along with the guy giving directions, goes too fast and does not explain.

I​nstructor compled each step a little too quickly quickly and I was not able to follow along in a timely manner. I had to keep pausing the video which, by the end of the project, left me no time to complete the final task of actually editing my resume and cover letter using the template that I had created. This Guided Project took way more than 40 minutes.
Great, clear and useful but, it needs some examples to fill the resume not just tips.
It's full of practical benefits •ᴗ• Masha'Allah. Thank God first, then thank Mr. Andres specially & U all generally.
Great Experience. Very Well Structured and targeted course. I recommend this course for every graduate/undergraduate student.
For me, this is the first course that I am taking in this field, but I am very optimistic. Thank you for those who contributed to the publication of this course.
